"{\"instruction\":\"Bu TypeScript kodundaki hatayi bul ve duzelt:\\n```typescript\\nclass Stack<T> {\\n    private items: T[] = [];\\n    \\n    push(item: T): void {\\n        this.items.push(item);\\n    }\\n    \\n    pop(): T {\\n        return this.items.pop();\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nconst stack = new Stack<number>();\\nstack.push(1);\\nstack.push(2);\\nconst val = stack.pop();\\nconsole.log(val.toFixed(2));  // runtime error!\\n```\",\"response\":\"class Stack<T> {\\n    private items: T[] = [];\\n    \\n    push(item: T): void {\\n        this.items.push(item);\\n    }\\n    \\n    pop(): T | undefined {\\n        return this.items.pop();\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nconst stack = new Stack<number>();\\nstack.push(1);\\nstack.push(2);\\nconst val = stack.pop();\\nif (val !== undefined) {\\n    console.log(val.toFixed(2));\\n}\",\"language\":\"typescript\",\"category\":\"bug_fix\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"bug_fix\"}"
