"{\"instruction\":\"Bu TypeScript kodundaki hatayi bul ve duzelt:\\n```typescript\\nenum Renk {\\n    KIRMIZI,\\n    YESIL,\\n    MAVI\\n}\\n\\nfunction renkKod(renk: Renk): string {\\n    return Renk[renk];\\n}\\n\\nconsole.log(renkKod(Renk.KIRMIZI));\\nconsole.log(renkKod(5));  // undefined ama hata yok!\\n```\",\"response\":\"enum Renk {\\n    KIRMIZI = 'kirmizi',\\n    YESIL = 'yesil',\\n    MAVI = 'mavi'\\n}\\n\\nfunction renkKod(renk: Renk): string {\\n    return renk;\\n}\\n\\nconsole.log(renkKod(Renk.KIRMIZI));\",\"language\":\"typescript\",\"category\":\"bug_fix\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"bug_fix\"}"
