"{\"instruction\":\"Bu Java kodundaki hatayi bul ve duzelt:\\n```java\\nimport java.util.concurrent.*;\\n\\npublic class Main {\\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        ExecutorService executor = Executors.newFixedThreadPool(10);\\n        executor.submit(() -> System.out.println(\\\"Islem\\\"));\\n    }\\n}\\n```\",\"response\":\"import java.util.concurrent.*;\\n\\npublic class Main {\\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        ExecutorService executor = Executors.newFixedThreadPool(10);\\n        try {\\n            executor.submit(() -> System.out.println(\\\"Islem\\\")).get();\\n        } catch (Exception e) {\\n            System.out.println(\\\"Hata: \\\" + e.getMessage());\\n        } finally {\\n            executor.shutdown();\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"bug_fix\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"bug_fix\"}"
