"{\"instruction\":\"Bu Java kodundaki hatayi bul ve duzelt:\\n```java\\nimport java.util.*;\\n\\npublic class Kullanici {\\n    String isim;\\n    \\n    @Override\\n    public boolean equals(Object o) {\\n        if (o instanceof Kullanici) {\\n            return isim.equals(((Kullanici) o).isim);\\n        }\\n        return false;\\n    }\\n    \\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Set<Kullanici> set = new HashSet<>();\\n        set.add(new Kullanici());\\n        System.out.println(set.contains(new Kullanici()));\\n    }\\n}\\n```\",\"response\":\"import java.util.*;\\n\\npublic class Kullanici {\\n    String isim;\\n    \\n    @Override\\n    public boolean equals(Object o) {\\n        if (this == o) return true;\\n        if (!(o instanceof Kullanici)) return false;\\n        Kullanici k = (Kullanici) o;\\n        return Objects.equals(isim, k.isim);\\n    }\\n    \\n    @Override\\n    public int hashCode() {\\n        return Objects.hash(isim);\\n    }\\n    \\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Set<Kullanici> set = new HashSet<>();\\n        Kullanici k = new Kullanici();\\n        k.isim = \\\"Ali\\\";\\n        set.add(k);\\n        Kullanici k2 = new Kullanici();\\n        k2.isim = \\\"Ali\\\";\\n        System.out.println(set.contains(k2));\\n    }\\n}\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"bug_fix\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"bug_fix\"}"
