"{\"instruction\":\"Bu Java kodundaki hatayi bul ve duzelt:\\n```java\\npublic class KilitOrnek {\\n    static final Object kilitA = new Object();\\n    static final Object kilitB = new Object();\\n    \\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Thread t1 = new Thread(() -> {\\n            synchronized (kilitA) {\\n                try { Thread.sleep(100); } catch (Exception e) {}\\n                synchronized (kilitB) { }\\n            }\\n        });\\n        Thread t2 = new Thread(() -> {\\n            synchronized (kilitB) {\\n                try { Thread.sleep(100); } catch (Exception e) {}\\n                synchronized (kilitA) { }\\n            }\\n        });\\n        t1.start(); t2.start();\\n    }\\n}\\n```\",\"response\":\"public class KilitOrnek {\\n    static final Object kilitA = new Object();\\n    static final Object kilitB = new Object();\\n    \\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\\n        Thread t1 = new Thread(() -> {\\n            synchronized (kilitA) {\\n                try { Thread.sleep(100); } catch (Exception e) {}\\n                synchronized (kilitB) { }\\n            }\\n        });\\n        Thread t2 = new Thread(() -> {\\n            synchronized (kilitA) {\\n                try { Thread.sleep(100); } catch (Exception e) {}\\n                synchronized (kilitB) { }\\n            }\\n        });\\n        t1.start(); t2.start();\\n    }\\n}\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"bug_fix\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"bug_fix\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"Bu Java kodundaki hatayi bul ve duzelt:\\n```java\\npublic class Sayac {\\n    static int sayac = 0;\\n    \\n    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\\n        Thread t1 = new Thread(() -> { for (int i = 0; i < 1000; i++) sayac++; });\\n        Thread t2 = new Thread(() -> { for (int i = 0; i < 1000; i++) sayac++; });\\n        t1.start(); t2.start();\\n        t1.join(); t2.join();\\n        System.out.println(sayac);  // 2000 olmali\\n    }\\n}\\n```\",\"response\":\"import java.util.concurrent.atomic.*;\\n\\npublic class Sayac {\\n    static AtomicInteger sayac = new AtomicInteger(0);\\n    \\n    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\\n        Thread t1 = new Thread(() -> { for (int i = 0; i < 1000; i++) sayac.incrementAndGet(); });\\n        Thread t2 = new Thread(() -> { for (int i = 0; i < 1000; i++) sayac.incrementAndGet(); });\\n        t1.start(); t2.start();\\n        t1.join(); t2.join();\\n        System.out.println(sayac.get());  // 2000\\n    }\\n}\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"bug_fix\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"bug_fix\"}"
