"{\"instruction\":\"Bir sifrenin guclugunu kontrol eden fonksiyon yaz\",\"response\":\"func SifreGuclugu(s string) int {\\n    puan := 0\\n    if len(s) >= 8 { puan++ }\\n    matched, _ := regexp.MatchString(`[a-z]`, s); if matched { puan++ }\\n    matched, _ = regexp.MatchString(`[A-Z]`, s); if matched { puan++ }\\n    matched, _ = regexp.MatchString(`\\\\d`, s); if matched { puan++ }\\n    matched, _ = regexp.MatchString(`[^\\\\w]`, s); if matched { puan++ }\\n    return puan\\n}\",\"language\":\"go\",\"category\":\"cross_lang\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"cross_lang\"}"
