"{\"instruction\":\"Bir tablodaki veriyi pivot yapan fonksiyon yaz\",\"response\":\"func PivotIslemi(data []map[string]interface{}, satir, sutun, deger string) map[string]map[string]interface{} {\\n    s := make(map[string]map[string]interface{})\\n    for _, r := range data {\\n        ri := r[satir].(string)\\n        si := r[sutun].(string)\\n        if s[ri] == nil { s[ri] = make(map[string]interface{}) }\\n        s[ri][si] = r[deger]\\n    }\\n    return s\\n}\",\"language\":\"go\",\"category\":\"cross_lang\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"cross_lang\"}"
