"{\"instruction\":\"Comparable implement eden Ogrenci sinifi yaz ve yasa gore sirala.\",\"response\":\"import java.util.*;\\nclass Ogrenci implements Comparable<Ogrenci> {\\n  String ad; int yas;\\n  Ogrenci(String ad, int yas) { this.ad=ad; this.yas=yas; }\\n  public int compareTo(Ogrenci o) { return Integer.compare(this.yas, o.yas); }\\n  public String toString() { return ad+\\\"-\\\"+yas; }\\n}\\nList<Ogrenci> liste = Arrays.asList(new Ogrenci(\\\"Ali\\\",25), new Ogrenci(\\\"Ayse\\\",20));\\nCollections.sort(liste);\\nSystem.out.println(liste);\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"manual\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"standard\"}"
