e if(s.equals(\\\"2\\\")) listele();\\n            else if(s.equals(\\\"3\\\")) { System.out.print(\\\"Index: \\\"); sil(Integer.parseInt(sc.nextLine())-1); }\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"project\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"project\"}"
