"{\"instruction\":\"JSON Veritabani Yoneticisi uygulamasi yap. Veri ekleme, silme, listeleme ve arama ozellikleri olsun. JSON tabanli CRUD islemleri yapan veritabani yoneticisi uygulamasi.\",\"response\":\"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html><head><meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\"><title>JSON Veritabani Yoneticisi</title></head><body>\\n<h1>JSON Veritabani Yoneticisi Uygulamasi</h1>\\n<input id=\\\"giris\\\" placeholder=\\\"Deger girin\\\">\\n<button onclick=\\\"ekle()\\\">Ekle</button>\\n<button onclick=\\\"listele()\\\">Listele</button>\\n<button onclick=\\\"temizle()\\\">Temizle</button>\\n<ul id=\\\"liste\\\"></ul>\\n<script>\\nvar veriler = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(\\\"veri\\\") || \\\"[]\\\");\\nfunction kaydet() { localStorage.setItem(\\\"veri\\\", JSON.stringify(veriler)); }\\nfunction ekle() { var d=document.getElementById(\\\"giris\\\").value; if(d){veriler.push(d);kaydet();document.getElementById(\\\"giris\\\").value=\\\"\\\";listele();} }\\nfunction listele() { document.getElementById(\\\"liste\\\").innerHTML=veriler.map(function(v,i){return \\\"<li>\\\"+(i+1)+\\\". \\\"+v+\\\" <button onclick='sil(\\\"+i+\\\")'>Sil</button></li>\\\";}).join(\\\"\\\"); }\\nfunction sil(i) { veriler.splice(i,1);kaydet();listele(); }\\nfunction temizle() { veriler=[];kaydet();listele(); }\\nlistele();\\n</script></body></html>\",\"language\":\"web\",\"category\":\"project\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"project\"}"
