"{\"instruction\":\"Bu kodda guvenlik acigi var mi? Coz:\\n```javascript\\napp.get(\\\"/f\\\",async(r,s)=>{const u=r.query.u;const d=await(await fetch(u)).text();s.send(d)})\\n```\",\"response\":\"Guvenlik acigi var. Cozumu:\\n```javascript\\napp.get(\\\"/f\\\",async(r,s)=>{const u=r.query.u;try{const p=new URL(u);if([\\\"localhost\\\",\\\"127.0.0.1\\\",\\\"0.0.0.0\\\"].includes(p.hostname))return s.status(403).send(\\\"no\\\");const d=await(await fetch(u,{signal:AbortSignal.timeout(5000)})).text();s.send(d)}catch{s.status(400).send(\\\"invalid\\\")}})\\n```\",\"language\":\"javascript\",\"category\":\"security\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"security\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"Bu kodda guvenlik acigi var mi? Coz:\\n```javascript\\napp.post(\\\"/p\\\",(r,s)=>{http.get(r.body.t,(re)=>re.pipe(s))})\\n```\",\"response\":\"Guvenlik acigi var. Cozumu:\\n```javascript\\napp.post(\\\"/p\\\",(r,s)=>{const p=new URL(r.body.t);if(/^(127|10|172\\\\.(1[6-9]|2\\\\\\\\d|3[01])|192\\\\.168)/.test(p.hostname))return s.status(403).send(\\\"no\\\");http.get(r.body.t,{timeout:5000},(re)=>re.pipe(s))})\\n```\",\"language\":\"javascript\",\"category\":\"security\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"security\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"Bu kodda guvenlik acigi var mi? Coz:\\n```java\\n@GetMapping(\\\"/f\\\")String f(@RequestParam String u)throws IOException{URL url=new URL(u);try(var r=new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(url.openStream()))){return r.lines().collect(Collectors.joining())}}\\n```\",\"response\":\"Guvenlik acigi var. Cozumu:\\n```java\\n@GetMapping(\\\"/f\\\")String f(@RequestParam String u)throws IOException{URI uri=new URI(u);String h=uri.getHost();if(h.equals(\\\"localhost\\\")||h.startsWith(\\\"10.\\\"))throw new SecurityException();HttpURLConnection c=(HttpURLConnection)uri.toURL().openConnection();c.setConnectTimeout(5000);try(var r=new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(c.getInputStream()))){return r.lines().collect(Collectors.joining())}}\\n```\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"security\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"security\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"Bu kodda guvenlik acigi var mi? Coz:\\n```java\\n@PostMapping(\\\"/pi\\\")ResponseEntity<byte[]>pi(@RequestParam String u)throws IOException{return ResponseEntity.ok(IOUtils.toByteArray(new URL(u)))}\\n```\",\"response\":\"Guvenlik acigi var. Cozumu:\\n```java\\n@PostMapping(\\\"/pi\\\")ResponseEntity<byte[]>pi(@RequestParam String u)throws IOException{URI uri=new URI(u);InetAddress a=InetAddress.getByName(uri.getHost());if(a.isSiteLocalAddress()||a.isLoopbackAddress())return ResponseEntity.status(403).build();HttpURLConnection c=(HttpURLConnection)uri.toURL().openConnection();c.setConnectTimeout(3000);return ResponseEntity.ok(IOUtils.toByteArray(c.getInputStream()))}\\n```\",\"language\":\"java\",\"category\":\"security\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"security\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"Bu kodda guvenlik acigi var mi? Coz:\\n```go\\nfunc f(w http.ResponseWriter,r*http.Request){url:=r.URL.Query().Get(\\\"u\\\");resp,_:=http.Get(url);defer resp.Body.Close();io.Copy(w,resp.Body)}\\n```\",\"response\":\"Guvenlik acigi var. Cozumu:\\n```go\\nfunc f(w http.ResponseWriter,r*http.Request){raw:=r.URL.Query().Get(\\\"u\\\");p,_:=url.Parse(raw);addrs,_:=net.LookupHost(p.Hostname());for_,a:=range addrs{ip:=net.ParseIP(a);if ip.IsPrivate()||ip.IsLoopback(){http.Error(w,\\\"no\\\",403);return}}c:=&http.Client{Timeout:5*time.Second};resp,err:=c.Get(raw);if err!=nil{http.Error(w,err.Error(),500);return}defer resp.Body.Close();io.Copy(w,resp.Body)}\\n```\",\"language\":\"go\",\"category\":\"security\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"security\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"Bu kodda guvenlik acigi var mi? Coz:\\n```go\\nfunc a(w http.ResponseWriter,r*http.Request){u:=r.FormValue(\\\"u\\\");resp,_:=http.Get(u);defer resp.Body.Close();d,_:=ioutil.ReadAll(resp.Body);w.Write(d)}\\n```\",\"response\":\"Guvenlik acigi var. Cozumu:\\n```go\\nfunc a(w http.ResponseWriter,r*http.Request){u:=r.FormValue(\\\"u\\\");p,_:=url.Parse(u);if!strings.HasPrefix(p.Host,\\\"cdn.x.com\\\"){http.Error(w,\\\"no\\\",403);return}c:=&http.Client{Timeout:5*time.Second};resp,err:=c.Get(u);if err!=nil{http.Error(w,\\\"err\\\",502);return}defer resp.Body.Close();d,_:=ioutil.ReadAll(resp.Body);w.Write(d)}\\n```\",\"language\":\"go\",\"category\":\"security\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"security\"}"
