"{\"instruction\":\"abc.ABC ve @abstractmethod ile soyut sinif.\",\"response\":\"from abc import ABC,abstractmethod\\nclass S(ABC):\\n  @abstractmethod\\n  def a(self): pass\\nclass Kare(S):\\n  def __init__(self,k): self.k=k\\n  def a(self): return self.k**2\\nprint(Kare(5).a())\",\"language\":\"python\",\"category\":\"standard\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"standard\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"functools.singledispatch ile tur bazli polimorfizm.\",\"response\":\"from functools import singledispatch\\n@singledispatch\\ndef y(a): print(f'Bilinmeyen: {a}')\\n@y.register(int)\\ndef _(a): print(f'Int: {a}')\\n@y.register(str)\\ndef _(a): print(f'Str: {a}')\\ny(42);y('Merhaba')\",\"language\":\"python\",\"category\":\"standard\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"standard\"}"
"{\"instruction\":\"functools.wraps ile decorator metadata.\",\"response\":\"from functools import wraps\\ndef log(f):\\n  @wraps(f)\\n  def w(*a,**k):\\n    print(f'{f.__name__} cagrildi')\\n    return f(*a,**k)\\n  return w\\n@log\\ndef t(a,b): return a+b\\nprint(t(3,5),t.__name__)\",\"language\":\"python\",\"category\":\"standard\",\"type\":\"manual\",\"format\":\"standard\"}"
